  "texts": [
    "First, the pool of users on ChatGPT is far larger, meaning we expect our data to be a closer approximation to the average chatbot user.",
    "4 Second, we use automated classifiers to report on the types of messages that users send using new classification taxonomies relative to the existing literature.",
    "Third, we report the diffusion of chatbot use across populations and the growth of different types of usage within cohorts.",
    "Fourth, we use a secure data clean room protocol to analyze aggregated employment and education categories for a sample of our users, lending new insights about differences in the types of messages sent by different groups while protecting user privacy.",
    "Our primary sample is a random selection of messages sent to ChatGPT on consumer plans (Free, Plus, Pro) between May 2024 and June 2025."
